@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = # Will be captured from signin response
@deviceId = # Will be set after getting device list

### Get all user devices
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get active user devices
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Approve a device (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Revoke a device (Admin or device owner)
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices/{{deviceId}}/revoke
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Clean up inactive devices (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

